A cat learning how to swim. AristoCats | 5 | Reviews Napoleon Bloodhound: Its squeaky shoes approaching. Lafayette Basset: Oh, cricket bugs don't wear shoes. AristoCats | 6 | Trivia Duchess: And your music is so different, so exciting. Berlioz kitten: It isn't Beethoven but it sure bounces. AristoCats | 7 | Comments Thomas O'Malley: But Madame's she's just another human. You're just her house pets. AristoCats | 8 | Quotes Madame Adelaide: They're the start of my new foundation.
